  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 178692792320
    m_Localized: Ms. Page
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 796530548736
    m_Localized: 'Pay coins to activate. Ms. Page draws with her magic pencil and
      triggers one random effect: gain 4 coins, send an opponent backward, or warp
      to any space you choose.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 863438086144
    m_Localized: Pawn
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 951233257472
    m_Localized: "By paying a set number of coins, this character calls in their
      friend \u201CThe Tower\u201D to temporarily block one of the paths at a split-path
      space for one turn. No shortcuts, no excuses\u2014just a very inconvenient
      tower."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1046301351936
    m_Localized: Rainbow Princess
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1088349249536
    m_Localized: By paying a set number of coins, this character can place sticky
      traps that latch onto any player who lands on them, immediately ending their
      turn. Each trap lasts for two turns, and only up to two can exist at the same
      time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2454555697152
    m_Localized: Robert
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2505575211008
    m_Localized: "By paying a set number of coins, this character goes on a full-speed
      sprint\u2014as if launched from a cannon\u2014charging forward five spaces.
      Along the way, they steal 5 coins from every player caught in their path. Sticky
      traps and Star Spaces? No problem. They\u2019re completely skipped, because
      nothing stops this sprint."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2539838480384
    m_Localized: Soldier Bryan
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2575922077696
    m_Localized: "This character\u2019s passive ability grants an extra coin when
      landing on Blue Spaces, and reduces the coin loss by one when landing on Red
      Spaces"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16500927471616
    m_Localized: Magic Drawing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16577045700608
    m_Localized: The Tower
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16646910222336
    m_Localized: Rainbow trap
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16711741579264
    m_Localized: Rock dash
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16789063573504
    m_Localized: Medal of Honor
